Package: ratingtables
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Table-Driven Rating Engine
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Greg", "Sollenberger", email = "yagreg7@yahoo.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A lightweight, dependency-free rating kernel for table-driven insurance rating. It supports long-form factor tables, specification-driven calculations, validation, optional traces, rate caps, and simple trace reshaping helpers.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
